title: Watch Derrick Henry's game-winning touchdown run against Tennessee
text:
Watch as one of the country's best running backs gives Alabama a lead they would not relinquish with a 14-yard touchdown run against the Tennessee Volunteers.
Henry finished the game with 28 carries for 143 yards, including the play in the video above.
